sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant SPA as SPA (app.js)
    participant Flask as server.py
    participant Bridge as bridge.py
    participant FS as commands/ dir
    participant VBA as Utilities.bas<br/>PollForCommandsTimer
    participant Macro as Target Macro

    User->>SPA: Click action or type chat command
    SPA->>Flask: POST /api/command {macro, args}
    Flask->>Bridge: send_command(macro, args)
    Bridge->>FS: Write {id}.json
    Bridge-->>Flask: Return command ID
    Flask-->>SPA: {command_id, status: pending}

    loop Every 2 seconds (Win32 SetTimer)
        VBA->>FS: Check for *.json files
    end

    VBA->>FS: Read {id}.json
    VBA->>Macro: Execute macro
    Macro-->>VBA: Return result
    VBA->>FS: Write {id}.result (UTF-8 via ADODB.Stream)
    VBA->>FS: Delete {id}.json

    loop Poll every 0.5s (up to 120s)
        SPA->>Flask: GET /api/command/{id}/result
        Flask->>Bridge: get_result(id)
        Bridge->>FS: Check for {id}.result
    end

    Bridge-->>Flask: Return result JSON
    Flask-->>SPA: {status, output}
    SPA-->>User: Display result
